@REPS_backend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5148

GET {{REPS_backend_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

# -----------------------
# LOGROS (ACHIEVEMENTS)
# -----------------------

### Obtener Logros de un Usuario (Dashboard/Comunidad)
GET {{REPS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/logro/user/1
Accept: application/json

### Obtener Logros Recientes (Dashboard)
GET {{REPS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/logro/recent/1
Accept: application/json

### Crear Logro (ADMIN - Requiere Token Bearer)
POST {{REPS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/logro
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <TU_TOKEN_ADMIN_AQUI>

{
  "titulo": "Racha de Fuego",
  "descripcion": "28 días consecutivos",
  "puntos": 50,
  "iconoUrl": "fire_icon.png"
}
